oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Oneida Highway Intersection
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Intersection where the Oneida Highway goes through Caryville. Highway 25 W is in the foreground.
The Cracker Barrel sits on the site of the house on the left of the Oneida Road. I-75 now cuts through mid-background.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
